compizconfig-python: compizconfig-python (Python Bindings for libcompizconfig)
compizconfig-python: 
compizconfig-python: Compiz-Fusion is a compositing window manager that uses 3D graphics 
compizconfig-python: acceleration via OpenGL. It provides various new graphical effects 
compizconfig-python: and features on any desktop environment, including GNOME. It is the 
compizconfig-python: result of the re-unification of the Beryl-project and the community 
compizconfig-python: around the Compiz Window Manager. 
compizconfig-python: 
compizconfig-python: This package provides Python bindings for the compiz-fusion 
compizconfig-python: configuration system.
